{"id":7001,"date":"2024-01-25T13:36:29","date_gmt":"2020-03-25T08:06:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=7001"},"modified":"2024-08-30T12:23:50","modified_gmt":"2024-08-30T06:53:50","slug":"bathroom-color-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-color-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Splish Splash In Style \u2013 Best Bathroom Colour Ideas For 2024!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>This is what your bathroom must look like in 2024 with these refreshing colour ideas<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your bathroom may not be the centrepiece of your home but is an essential part of it; the slightest change can feel overwhelming. However, like every other space in your home your bathroom deserves a radical makeover. We\u2019d say they are ideal spaces for a pinch of panache. And considering they are much smaller than bedrooms, even a small change here and there can magically transform it. Changing the colour scheme of your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">bathroom interiors<\/a> is a smart way to do this!&nbsp; So what are the splashing colours ideas for bathrooms this year? Well, we do know them. Here are 10 bathroom colour ideas that are.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White And Navy&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The all white bathroom with a pop of navy blue designed with open shelf storage makes this space an elegant and refreshing to look at. This particular pairing, that is slightly soft and wee a bit shiny, works well with wooden cabinetry and mirrors. The drawers under the sink in navy blue bring in a striking contrast to an otherwise stalk white bathroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013650\/white-navy-with-wood-bathroom-color-combinations.jpg\" alt=\"White and Navy bathroom colors make space an elegant and refreshing to look at. \" class=\"wp-image-7014\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013650\/white-navy-with-wood-bathroom-color-combinations.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013650\/white-navy-with-wood-bathroom-color-combinations-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013650\/white-navy-with-wood-bathroom-color-combinations-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013650\/white-navy-with-wood-bathroom-color-combinations-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/white-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">White Bathroom Design Ideas For Your home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Grey And White<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For all those in love with minimalist trends then this is the ultimate colour combination for you. Grey and white complement each other beautifully and also stand out when introduced alone. Notice the wall tiles here? An elegant mix of white and grey that blend together so smoothly. A white ladder with shelves has been used to store linen and wooden cabinets make the aesthetics sharply appealing.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013629\/grey-white-bathroom-paint-colors.jpg\" alt=\"Grey and white bathroom paint color complement each other beautifully and also stand out when introduced alone.\" class=\"wp-image-7009\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013629\/grey-white-bathroom-paint-colors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013629\/grey-white-bathroom-paint-colors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013629\/grey-white-bathroom-paint-colors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013629\/grey-white-bathroom-paint-colors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White, Pink And Copper<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This pairing is warm and welcoming with copper accents that complement it. It&#8217;s also an excellent pick for modern-day houses, and not to forget perfect for single women. All the credit goes to its fun and light vibe. Who wouldn\u2019t feel refreshed here<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013655\/white-pink-bathroom-colors.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom color ideas with white and pink pairing is warm and welcoming with copper accents that complement it.\" class=\"wp-image-7015\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013655\/white-pink-bathroom-colors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013655\/white-pink-bathroom-colors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013655\/white-pink-bathroom-colors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013655\/white-pink-bathroom-colors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Green, White And Gold<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you love everything classic and often find yourself drawn to whites and creams then this one\u2019s for you. Just to mix things up a bit we have here a bathroom in a colour palette of green and white. This is a fresh take on all things classic and natural. This pairing makes this bathroom look spacious and gives its close counterparts a tough fight. A gold mirror and fixtures to match luxe it up.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013624\/green-white-gold-bathroom-colors.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom paint colors with green and white make the bathroom look spacious and gives its close counterparts a tough fight.\" class=\"wp-image-7008\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013624\/green-white-gold-bathroom-colors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013624\/green-white-gold-bathroom-colors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013624\/green-white-gold-bathroom-colors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013624\/green-white-gold-bathroom-colors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sparkling White, A Monochrome Colour Idea<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a colour that never goes out of style. There&#8217;s nothing more luxurious than the colour white for your bathroom. Hints of cream and ivory accents add subtle glam to this space. Boldly layer these shades of the same family with wicker baskets for your laundry and cabinetry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013642\/sparking-white-bathroom-color-design.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom wall colors sparkling white is more luxurious than other colors.\" class=\"wp-image-7012\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013642\/sparking-white-bathroom-color-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013642\/sparking-white-bathroom-color-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013642\/sparking-white-bathroom-color-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013642\/sparking-white-bathroom-color-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black With A Plant Wall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you wish to make an edgy statement with your bathroom? An astonishing black bathroom will turn heads. If you are ready to go with this daring colour, consider greenery on a wall behind the sink as we see in this image. This balancing act of black with hints of greenery and the warm glow of focused lighting binds the space together seamlessly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013613\/black-with-plant-wall-bathroom-paint-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Black bathroom wall paint with a plant wall and the warm glow of focused lighting binds the space together seamlessly.\" class=\"wp-image-7006\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013613\/black-with-plant-wall-bathroom-paint-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013613\/black-with-plant-wall-bathroom-paint-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013613\/black-with-plant-wall-bathroom-paint-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013613\/black-with-plant-wall-bathroom-paint-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beige And Gold<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you someone who relishes luxury and doesn\u2019t mind flaunting it? Well, this is right up your alley.&nbsp; This duo is everything luxury can offer. This pairing gives you ample scope to play around with. Incorporate shades of beige in your bathroom interiors and highlight it with gold accents for a seven-star feel!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013608\/beige-gold-bathroom-paint.jpg\" alt=\"Beige and gold bathroom color design this duo is everything luxury can offer.\" class=\"wp-image-7005\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013608\/beige-gold-bathroom-paint.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013608\/beige-gold-bathroom-paint-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013608\/beige-gold-bathroom-paint-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013608\/beige-gold-bathroom-paint-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a free design consultation, call our designers\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28125622\/do-you-want-free-design-consultation.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mauve, Rose And Gold<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This duo will remind you of spring! It is easily paired with a lot of shades but looks absolutely ravishing when paired with rose gold accents and white. Adding to the bathroom\u2019s paradise-like feel are plants, lots of lights, and a stark white bathtub. Rose petals anyone<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013633\/rose-gold-bathroom-wall-colors.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom color combinations mauve, rose and gold this duo will remind you of spring!\" class=\"wp-image-7010\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013633\/rose-gold-bathroom-wall-colors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013633\/rose-gold-bathroom-wall-colors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013633\/rose-gold-bathroom-wall-colors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013633\/rose-gold-bathroom-wall-colors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sky Blue And Grey<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We all know that dark colours make spaces look smaller, so this pairing is perfect for small bathrooms. Grey and white tiled floors paired with sky blue cabinetry looks refreshing, doesn\u2019t it? Keeping the charm intact are patterned tiles on a wall behind the sink that add a splash of design as seen in this image.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013637\/sky-blue-grey-bathroom-wall-paint.jpg\" alt=\"Best bathroom colors grey and white tiled floors paired with sky blue cabinetry looks refreshing.\" class=\"wp-image-7011\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013637\/sky-blue-grey-bathroom-wall-paint.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013637\/sky-blue-grey-bathroom-wall-paint-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013637\/sky-blue-grey-bathroom-wall-paint-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013637\/sky-blue-grey-bathroom-wall-paint-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sunshine Yellow&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This delightfully bright bathroom is ideal for those who revel in everything bold. Yellow as a colour scheme for your bathroom interiors, contrary to popular belief, will not make your eyes clinch. Just the right pairing with mirrors, white accents, a dash of wooden cabinetry, and cove lighting behind makes this bathroom a happy place to bathe in!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013646\/sunshine-yellow-best-bathroom-colors.jpg\" alt=\"Sunshine yellow bathroom colors delightfully bright bathroom is ideal for those who revel in everything bold.\" class=\"wp-image-7013\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013646\/sunshine-yellow-best-bathroom-colors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013646\/sunshine-yellow-best-bathroom-colors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013646\/sunshine-yellow-best-bathroom-colors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21013646\/sunshine-yellow-best-bathroom-colors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And with that it\u2019s a wrap. Pick a colour for your bathroom that matches your style and your requirements. You don&#8217;t want any part of your dream home to look dull or unattractive. Find a colour scheme for your bathroom that\u2019s right for you. Just make sure you keep it clean, tidy and presentable all the time. Happy colouring!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you need some more tips? Book a consultation with us here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/red-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">Red Bathroom Ideas<\/a><\/li>